lyrics:
[verse]
As the neon lights flicker, memories ignite
I'm lost in a haze, swimming through the night
Your face haunts my dreams, like a ghost from the past
Reflecting on the love we've lost, it seems to forever last

[chorus]
Oh, these echoes of yesterday, they won't let me be
Whispering secrets of the love that used to set me free
In this electronic dreamland, my heart's immersed in sorrow
Forever reflecting on the beauty we shared, now gone tomorrow
